<p>This year's 31 contestants are AJ, 28, a software salesman from Playa del Rey, California, Army ranger veteran Ben, 29, from Venice, California, wealth management consultant Bennett, 36, from New York City, and male grooming specialist Blake Monar, 31, from Phoenix, Arizona.</p>

